  Requirements:
    php 5.2.4 or later
    MySQL 5.0.45 or later
    a web-browser (duh!)

  Summary:
    Pragyan CMS is used to handle the creation, updation and administration of a website.
    For a summary of features, please see the Documentation.txt file.

  Download:
    You can get the newest version at http://sf.net/projects/pragyan

  Credits:
    Please see the INSTALL/Documentation.txt file.

  Installation:
    Please see the INSTALL/INSTALL.txt file.

